Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:02:00.05,title_op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(942,658.5)\fad(500,0)}SKY RESORT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡过头啦～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为昨天和莉娜畅聊了一个通宵…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.70,0:02:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的我在干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服送去洗了还没拿回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.89,0:02:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉…莉欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前…前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥是龙虾装？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你非常相衬啊 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊莉欧 你不是有其他的衣服可以穿的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太赶了 所以看到什么就随手抓什么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.57,0:02:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一般人随手也不会抓这个的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这样 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你们知道明天空中度假村就要全面开业了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是山顶上的那个三角形东西吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是日后霍华德度假村的支柱 全新的综合娱乐设施
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中度假村
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:57.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sky Resort
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算以世界最高的赌场作为其卖点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想说它是这个岛上最高的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我想让你们从今天开始 在空中度假村工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你们能在最高的舞台展示出最棒的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带一提 虽然那里没有赌场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过世界最高的城市是海拔约4070米的波多西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:24.57,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}波多西（Potosi）：玻利维亚城市，\N人口仅11万，曾以盛产银矿出名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开业时间是明日正午
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前把你们的个人房间给退了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到新住处去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「胸震震拳击」还是「油溜溜摔跤」好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的开业盛典 就这个还不太够
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「肉弹弹沙滩夺旗赛」…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字听起来有点像肥肉啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫「乳摇摇」如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊！叫「炸裂！最强美女Dealer姐妹！」吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…但是这样别人就听不懂了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「死或生的天堂」也挺好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个电梯外的景色总是那么棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来还真是突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听他口气好像会有一个很大的惊喜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没去过那 好期待明天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那之前还要搬家 真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也没太多行李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮娅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你是行李
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我不是这个意思啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来已经很热闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌场是在这上面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为之前一直不许进入 我们今天也是第一次来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到外面！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是海啊 莉欧前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:05:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边看又会怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 因为我经常摔…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎！等好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫琳达 是空中度假村的专用Dealer哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板让我给小莉欧你们带路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于空中度假村的问题啥都能回答你们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件衣服是老板的癖好？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是空中度假村引以为豪的赌场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都闪闪发亮的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在闪光光吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:47.42,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Howard Resort！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 去看下一个！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:05:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个大厅是干啥用的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是全息影院哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足不出户就可以在各种世界中探险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去很危险的 小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去下一个地方啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下 下一个？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好逼真的虚拟空间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.93,0:06:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像真的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过嘛 某种角度上说是真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是掉下去会怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概会很疼吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有安全系统在 小命大概还是保得住的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉欧 这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳达只要打个响指就能做到各种事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是霍华德度假村引以为豪的卖点之一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极限滑道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个滑道的管道可是遍布整个空中度假村的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.57,0:06:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是名副其实的世界上最长滑道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:06:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣的样子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中度假村实在太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你们也记不住全部的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有些暂时不能用的设施
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过多少知道大概了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真是受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要开业了还乱堆东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去下一个地方啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳达力气真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看那都超出力气大这个定义了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是啊 她到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有什么疑问吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳达小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下来了～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天敲自己背的时候 卡着头的连接松掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道是…机器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dealer机器人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我身上还有空中度假村主控电脑的终端哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你打个响指就能做到各种事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说 这样你也没必要打响指吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴露了啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥啊 是介么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虾米玩意啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对对…对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连吐槽都可以的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起 对不起 对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊！那玩意不好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下的脑袋不是西兰花！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更好吃的要看看这份邀请书…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是花椰菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天霍华德度假村 又迎来了一个新的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其名为 空中度假村！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是用最新最强的技术建造的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:09:00.90,A6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}…配有赌场…不 是所有娱乐设施的新一代度假村
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗纱小姐一定很不甘心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:09:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 居然在这么有纪念意义的日子里有拍摄工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我汤姆·霍华德向诸位保证
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位将在这个空中度假村
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体会到前所未有的震撼和感动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我身为主控单元也该去干活了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底她这算不算高科技呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 也是个挺有意思的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能一起工作的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物以类聚？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在经常跌倒这点上很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这太直接了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？说啥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻开始的体验会在后世中流传下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冗长的演说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我随时都行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中度假村 开业！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前 前辈 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面离我们越来越远了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信 我们在不断向天空中升上去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:11:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 所以这里才叫空中度假村啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么诸位 请入场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是空中度假村！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内部负重增加的确认完成了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口的计数器如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个0 好了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人剩下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认全部人都已经入场 于是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 封锁完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空情况如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路畅通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统全部正常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中度假村 出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海拔500尺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好猛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们飘起来了 飘起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到这么大的东西可以飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是飞在空中的赌场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到空中度假村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然踏上旅途了啊 莉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就搞好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 这里是禁止进入的 不能进来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你迷路了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找大姐姐你有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在世界上最高的地方开设的赌场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是空中度假村
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颠覆之前的所有常识
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个巨大的建筑物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为闪耀的娱乐天堂 此刻正进行它的升空之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请在这个超酷超棒的赌场中 尽情享受吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 又中了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天手气这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因为我在这浮在空中 离天国最近的赌场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是多亏了在我们面前的女神大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天胜利的女神的力量超强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是因为靠近天国啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了 你下手轻点啊小莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算浮在空中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你抓住的也不该是云 而应该是运气才是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要再来不？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 再来一局！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳达小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小莉欧 小莉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小莉欧 琳达要挑战你 要挑战你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑战？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.93,0:15:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 是用Gate Battle 是用Gate Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gate？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是Gate Battle 是Gate Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳达要挑战你 要挑战你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又 又来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得琳达的样子怪怪的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊琳达小姐 你是Gate Holder啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gate Holder 是Holder
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.74,0:15:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她又在说两遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说两遍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说Gate Battle？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我接受这场对局！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个台词 他又要来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是在等着这样的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空中度假村初次营业的时候 载入史册的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了Gate Battle外 别无他选！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.22,0:16:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我说…我又是不做不行吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这全都是为了今日到场的嘉宾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉欧 我们霍华德度假村的宗旨是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「悉从客人所愿」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 莉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板 对战方法是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无疑问 是用空中度假村的经典 极限滑道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这泳衣感觉好猛…它不会滑掉吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常适合你们啊 两位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了客人们 加油哦两位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:16:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我将从这里 从空中度假村
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给大家带来莉欧前辈对阵琳达小姐的Gate Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实况转播是我 阿妮娅·赫尔辛格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解说是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏特小姐 巧可 还有蒂芙妮小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场比赛 双方分别赌上了两张和一张的Gate来战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就让我们通过艾露小姐和伊露小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看看滑道的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样 顺着滑道滑下去 最先到达终点的人赢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑道有着各种各样不同的分叉路线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然无论选择哪条路线全长都基本相同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因应路线不同 倾斜角和加速度也不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路线的选择是获胜的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中也有些路线不要去选哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而如果选了的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 终于要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会输的不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳达你果然有点怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gate Battle哦 集中注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.02,0:18:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 倒数开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上喽！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初始加速势均力敌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场比赛 对空中度假村了如指掌的琳达小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟还是更有优势吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 莉欧是这个霍华德度假村的胜利之女神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信她一定会获胜的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 到此路线就开始分叉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉欧很好地利用了大角度的路线 一口气加速了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉欧前辈选择了赌场路线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而琳达小姐则进入了泳池路线！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！琳达也追上来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到下一个分岔路口了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！前辈选择了有利的空中路线！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有利么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 她抛开不少了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招看招～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会输的不会输的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这下厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳达小姐利用身为空中度假村的主电脑这点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快地追上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直逼莉欧前辈了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上了 追上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 好激烈的缠斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 俩人正向着终点逼近！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获胜的是哪位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goal！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获胜的是…琳…哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goal！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获胜的是莉欧前辈！
